<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 12:25:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普模因币在海湖庄园活动上大放异彩，营销总统</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/trump-memecoin-jumps-on-mar-a-lago-event-marketing-the-president</link><description>带有唐纳德·特朗普名字的模因币在过去 24 小时内飙升了 60%，此前其发起人在海湖庄园举办了一场以总统为主角的独家晚会广告后，尽管白宫尚未证实他将出席。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iwYGTmF8jOWE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 20:14:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/trump-memecoin-jumps-on-mar-a-lago-event-marketing-the-president</guid></item><item><title>比特币触及近期交易区间顶部后涨幅回落</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-edges-higher-in-asia-despite-middle-east-jitters</link><description>随着中东动荡继续冲击全球市场，比特币攀升至近期交易区间的上限，之后最大的加密货币回吐涨幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivgEuwjOyR4A/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 02:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-edges-higher-in-asia-despite-middle-east-jitters</guid></item><item><title>比特币接近过去熊市触底的区域</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-nears-zone-where-past-bear-markets-have-bottomed-out</link><description>一位曾投资过之前三个繁荣和萧条周期的加密货币基金经理表示，自 10 月份以来，比特币的价值已损失了近一半，历史上标志着过去低迷结束的一系列指标表明，抛售可能正在进入最后阶段。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i7haQl9CopKU/v1/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 14:29:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-nears-zone-where-past-bear-markets-have-bottomed-out</guid></item><item><title>Ramp 收购 Billhop，计划在欧洲和英国扩张</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/ramp-acquires-billhop-plans-expansion-across-europe-and-uk</link><description>Ramp Inc. 正在利用斯德哥尔摩的一项收购来打开欧洲市场，购买支付公司 Billhop 及其监管许可证，将其价值 320 亿美元的金融运营平台带到大西洋彼岸。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9wNkRRjbHeo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/ramp-acquires-billhop-plans-expansion-across-europe-and-uk</guid></item><item><title>随着伊朗战争的继续，迪拜加密货币活动 Token2049 被推迟</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/dubai-crypto-event-token2049-postponed-as-iran-war-continues</link><description>全球最大的加密货币会议之一 Token2049 将不再按计划在下个月举行迪拜活动，因为阿拉伯联合酋长国和其他中东国家面临着来自伊朗的持续导弹袭击。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iAz.AkbpC1bY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/dubai-crypto-event-token2049-postponed-as-iran-war-continues</guid></item><item><title>Tether 花费数十亿美元在华盛顿寻找新盟友</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2026-tether-usa-crypto-ambitions/</link><description>这家加密货币公司的亿万富翁首席执行官表示，在政府最高层的支持、1220 亿美元的美国国债和一家正在建设中的美国新企业的支持下，Tether 将会继续存在。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iT6R8.a.9t2s/v3/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2026-tether-usa-crypto-ambitions/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行和渣打银行将在香港获得稳定币牌照</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/hsbc-standard-chartered-to-get-stablecoin-licenses-in-hong-kong</link><description>汇丰控股有限公司和渣打银行将成为香港首批获得许可的稳定币发行人之一，使香港的两家发钞银行在政府成为数字资产中心的努力中发挥核心作用。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igDAxrKVR_V0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 05:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/hsbc-standard-chartered-to-get-stablecoin-licenses-in-hong-kong</guid></item><item><title>加密货币交易所押注预测市场以度过熊市</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-12/crypto-exchanges-eye-prediction-markets-stock-trading-to-survive-bear-market</link><description>要么做大，要么回家。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyP5aCxFbnMw/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-12/crypto-exchanges-eye-prediction-markets-stock-trading-to-survive-bear-market</guid></item><item><title>Tether Investment 首席执行官在主导交易热潮后辞职</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/tether-investments-chief-to-step-down-after-leading-deals-spree</link><description>Tether Holdings SA 首席投资官理查德·希思科特 (Richard Heathcote) 负责监督支持其主要稳定币的巨额储备，以及涉及从足球俱乐部到人形机器人等各种领域的交易热潮，他即将辞去职务。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFyR5_uXgrOs/v0/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 18:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/tether-investments-chief-to-step-down-after-leading-deals-spree</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争导致油价飙升至 100 美元以上，比特币走弱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-surges-back-above-100-on-iran-war</link><description>由于对伊朗冲突的担忧加深，油价短暂回升至每桶 100 美元以上，比特币波动接近近期价格水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/imyQrgW3agvE/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 04:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-surges-back-above-100-on-iran-war</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行行长帕内塔表示私营部门是跨境支付的关键</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/ecb-s-panetta-says-private-sector-key-in-cross-border-payments</link><description>欧洲央行管理委员会成员法比奥·帕内塔表示，私营部门将在确保跨境支付的未来方面发挥关键作用。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iaUstt.aNd.c/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 15:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/ecb-s-panetta-says-private-sector-key-in-cross-border-payments</guid></item></channel></rss>